                                                        <h3 class="font-bold my-3 text-2xl xl:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl tracking-[0px]">The journey begins.</h3>
                                                        <p class="text-black text-base md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl 2xl:text-2xl">Our founders launched a college startup in 2012, named Applits, with a bold vision: revolutionize the mobile app industry through crowdsourced app ideas. The Applits community submitted concepts for the next big app, and public votes decided which ideas came to fruition. With initial funding, we aimed to grow the community and outsourced app development to established agencies.</p>
