                                                        <p class="text-black text-base md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl 2xl:text-2xl">It became clear to us what to do next: we decided to close Applits so we could forge our own agency to solve these exact problems. Following the classic “necessity is the mother of invention” philosophy, we built what we wish we could have found as paying clients years ago. We have poured over our process to identify the key actions and steps for success when building custom software for demanding consumers, and doing so with an eye for making it the best possible experience for our clients.</p>
